column5: Have enjoyed reading the posts for quite a while now and thought maybe it was time to introduce myself and help contribute to the board. I live out east and am an avid Steelheader spring and fall, Salmon in Lake Ontario in the summer and ice fishing in the winter. Hopefully somewhere along the way I can help keep this board as interesting as it is.Looking forward to talking to you in the future.  Backlash
Welcome to OFC Backlash You've made to right choice.... best site on the planet Looking forward to your futur reports Leechman
Welcome aboard your at the right site Backlash
Welcome to the site  ...looking forward to seeing some nice Lake O Salmon reports next year
